    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Parades consisting of floats, vehicles, boats, or participants that are decorated or covered with flowers. Floats are usually designed to illustrate a theme or represent a group, and are often judged in a competition following the parade itself.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
